  <p class="staffTitle">Making aid more transparent</p>
  <p class="staffBio"> Since 2010, Akvo has been collaborating with USAID as part of the Dutch and United States governments' cooperation in the field of water. Akvo is part of an open data working group established between the USAID and the World Bank. USAID is co-funding a programme of the Millennium Water Alliance, which is using Akvo RSR and Akvo FLOW to improve transparency, in Kenya. In conjunction with Aqua4All, Akvo is in the process of extending and intensifying this partnership.</p>
</div>
<div class="extLoad" id="cardno">
